871d5752996f0b0149c3ce1","tid":1461801,"uid":30697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:47:01.000Z","msg":"[和理非］<br />\n<br />\n各位 請聽我講 我地唔好直接搬路障阻住旅客check in 或者做破壞<br />\n咁樣只會損壞我地呢次和理非既形象<br />\n我地要醒d等政府自己取消航班<br />\n<br />\n大家抗爭要顧住形象ar!!!<br />\n唔好同旅客爭執 我地要爭取國際認同<br />\n如果國際言論都唔支持我地 我地就輸ge la<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<br />\n<br />\n人多自然佢就會停 我地係要人多 唔係同旅客爭執"},{"pid":"3976817b4294212fe918af1ea6ecaf153ff55ed3","tid":1461801,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:47:05.000Z","msg":"根本唔使阻<br />\n政府會停飛"},{"pid":"9404637a36292d795809c5c28ef1cca521887981","tid":1461801,"uid":69419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:47:12.000Z","msg":"機場，一定要搞。<br />\n因為對準經濟，完全正確！<br />\n<br />\n但係一旦有人搞事，就過去隔開問清楚咩事，睇返毅進仔討論能力奇差，佢哋實唔夠講<br />\n<br />\n怪錯個旅客要say sorry, 我地唔係要樹敵<br />\n我地要拎attention<br />\n尤其是國際attention/support"},{"pid":"7f406558c2b4d19705c3c5cceb2f06c084e86b16","tid":1461801,"uid":241844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:47:57.000Z","msg":"一直就算封到琴日都係想宣傳同集會，琴日癱左次，今日就要癱？ 地鐵都無咁做啦 邊有得迫嫁 咪玩啦"},{"pid":"54e3feba080f72fbf29189bceec511231ba7bd14","tid":1461801,"uid":11017,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:48:44.000Z","msg":"屌你老母 你地14年訓撚到E家呀?<br />\n14年夠好形象未 夠國際支持未 咪又係輸到仆街"},{"pid":"4d728603a681b74ea803b2a0eb31a2c565428128","tid":1461801,"uid":269617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df56ab59f2eca84ba59e4269a3bedb6e7b0f3022","tid":1461801,"uid":135274,"like":78,"dislike":4,"score":74,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:20:34.000Z","msg":"<strong>注意琴日機場癱瘓既原因，係交通</strong>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:49:17.000Z","msg":"我識做"},{"pid":"77aa071fe1e75b035590de6060a32750790f2a63","tid":1461801,"uid":198623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:50:02.000Z","msg":"both"},{"pid":"0377f09280b2a437ab2165762fe1d10bb31271df","tid":1461801,"uid":280004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:50:07.000Z","msg":"主宣傳，人多先癱瘓<br />\n<br />\nbe humble, be polite"},{"pid":"d83ed7f498fbf556aac10c04e44cb77f7b7973cb","tid":1461801,"uid":275055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:50:42.000Z","msg":"根本兩樣都有，啲咁嘅post只係為左分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85b47fe2d698991a988fe029c8bcae0125d29585","tid":1461801,"uid":294605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:51:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">WHERE AMAZING JOURNEYS BEGIN</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新口號, 神助攻</span></span><br />\n<br />\nfrom HKIA front page"},{"pid":"89451851bde8cbde129a17b57cad0c61799aea51","tid":1461801,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:51:20.000Z","msg":"Y not both<br />\n少人宣傳<br />\n多人宣傳加癱疲<br />\n無嘢輸"},{"pid":"f995f4180b880b524b77480d778234c67dfd45f0","tid":1461801,"uid":69587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:52:28.000Z","msg":"去宣傳"},{"pid":"ba626c041e764967d98e1ad21dfe8836c8ed2439","tid":1461801,"uid":52574,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:53:04.000Z","msg":"Why not both？<br />\n你地估接機就真係和理非咁簡單咩......係有藉口掩飾你地衝離境啊！<br />\n「arrival唔夠位 爆左所以我咪去departure靜坐囉」<br />\n明唔明係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">人數取勝被動塞</span></span>先係最legit<br />\n而家夾硬阻礙人地出入 只會變左非法禁錮人<br />\n成個行動唔legit 同塞鐵一樣 小貓三四隻塞目的唔太達到又唔legit<br />\n其實琴日癱瘓最大原因從來唔係塞Departure（要知道仲有通道留俾人自由進出），而係交通 + 有機組人員自發罷工<br />\n罷工係基本法賦予嘅權利，但我地限制人地人身自由係變咗剝削人地權利+非法禁錮<br />\n我明大家好想重現琴日癱瘓畫面，但而家人數真係唔夠！！好應該忍下手俾d耐性唔好俾憤怒沖昏頭腦啊！！<br />\n衝左入禁區，一陣有咩事，個單眼女義士都唔安樂！！<br />\n唔好俾情緒主導，癱瘓固然重要 但可以<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更有智慧地癱而且唔遭人話柄！</span></span><br />\n要接受我地係長期抗爭！其實最應該係煲大某幾日搞大佢配合機組人員罷工（呢個係關鍵），到時你慢慢塞都冇問題！！<br />\n<br />\n我地而家唔係要搞到<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「旅客上唔到機」</span></strong></span><br />\n而要係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>「班機起唔到飛」</strong></span></span>！"},{"pid":"9c3341241715fe8e63e54e4fcded866a23579ef3","tid":1461801,"uid":184783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:53:18.000Z","msg":"[理性討論] 有死線前提搞機場/隔日搞機場比日日搞更好<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1459515\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1459515</a>"},{"pid":"3fd33bfffe5ca80b69ff40467f5bfb1026718342","tid":1461801,"uid":271051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:54:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">BOTH</span></span>"},{"pid":"a94c3539618fb1aa4351754e6cb7cfd967d6de9c","tid":1461801,"uid":28163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"咪撚左膠住<br />\n宣傳....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n敵人打我<br />\n我宣傳"},{"pid":"607e8304ca7c5b05d61c5fddeab907fc1745ac20","tid":1461801,"uid":90012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:56:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"139ef90bd6ef718e1ee051671817a07c5ed917a4","tid":1461801,"uid":282786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:57:01.000Z","msg":"主癱瘓副宣傳   但係癱瘓係要用人數塞爆個機場   而唔係夾尻硬擋撚住遊客唔比人走   要走就比佢走   做返自己野   只要夠多人令到全部機停飛佢地自然無得走   唔需要你去擋佢"},{"pid":"481f6255541aa5a1004706eee779bf4e8e873961","tid":1461801,"uid":13187,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a94c3539618fb1aa4351754e6cb7cfd967d6de9c","tid":1461801,"uid":28163,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:55:11.000Z","msg":"咪撚左膠住<br />\n宣傳....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n敵人打我<br />\n我宣傳"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T09:57:41.000Z","msg":"依家係旅客打你咩？<br />\n咁勇武機場唔啱你"},{"pi